    </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>Metody</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/Async_scripts\">Użycie async skryptów dla asm.js</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/Apps/Developing/Optimizing_startup_performance\">Optimizing startup performance</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/WebRTC_data_channels\">Using WebRTC peer-to-peer data channels</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/Efficient_animation_for_web_games\">Efektywne animacje dla gier wideo</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/Audio_for_Web_Games\">Audio dla gier internetowych</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/2D_collision_detection\">2D collision detection</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/Tilemaps\">Tiles and tilemaps overview</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>3D games on the Web</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/3D_on_the_web\">3D games on the Web overview</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/3D_on_the_web/Basic_theory\">Explaining basic 3D theory</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/3D_on_the_web/Building_up_a_basic_demo_with_A-Frame\">Tworzenie podstawowego demo z A-Frame</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/3D_on_the_web/Building_up_a_basic_demo_with_Babylon.js\">Tworzenie podstawowego demo z Babylon.js</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/3D_on_the_web/Building_up_a_basic_demo_with_PlayCanvas\">Tworzenie podstawowego demo z PlayCanvas</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/3D_on_the_web/Building_up_a_basic_demo_with_Three.js\">Tworzenie podstawowego demo z Three.js</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/3D_on_the_web/WebVR\">WebVR</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/3D_collision_detection\">3D collision detection</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/3D_collision_detection/Bounding_volume_collision_detection_with_THREE.js\">Bounding volume collision detection with THREE.js</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>Implementing game control mechanisms</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/Control_mechanisms\">Control mechanisms</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/Control_mechanisms/Mobile_touch\">Mobile touch</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/Control_mechanisms/Desktop_with_mouse_and_keyboard\">Desktop with mouse and keyboard</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/Control_mechanisms/Desktop_with_gamepad\">Desktop with gamepad</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Techniques/Control_mechanisms/Other\">Other</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>Samouczki</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_Breakout_game_pure_JavaScript\">2D breakout game using pure JavaScript</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_breakout_game_Phaser\">2D breakout game using Phaser</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Tutorials/HTML5_Gamedev_Phaser_Device_Orientation\">2D maze_game with device orientation</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"https://mozdevs.github.io/html5-games-workshop/en/guides/platformer/start-here/\">2D platform game using Phaser</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n        <details>\n            <summary>Publikacja gier</summary>\n            <ol>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Publishing_games\">Publishing games overview</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Publishing_games/Game_distribution\">Game distribution</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Publishing_games/Game_promotion\">Game promotion</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Publishing_games/Game_monetization\">Game monetization</a></li>\n            </ol>\n        </details>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"></div>\n\n<p>Ta strona zawiera poradniki, które wyróżniają wiele sposobów pracy w celu skutecznego wszelkiego rodzaju gier internetowych.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"gra_breakout_2d_w_czystym_javascript\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_Breakout_game_pure_JavaScript\">Gra Breakout 2D w czystym&nbsp;JavaScript</a></dt>\n <dd>W tym poradniku krok po kroku stworzysz prosty klon gry Breakout napisany&nbsp;w całości w czystym języku JavaScript. Nauczysz się podstaw używania elementu <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> do implementowania podstawowych mechanik gry jak renderowanie, przesuwanie grafik, wykrywanie kolizji, mechanizmu sterowania oraz stanu wygrania/przegrania.&nbsp;</dd>\n <dt id=\"2d_breakout_game_using_phaser\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Tutorials/2D_breakout_game_Phaser\">2D breakout game using Phaser</a></dt>\n <dd>In this step-by-step tutorial you'll implement the same breakout clone as the previous tutorial series, except that this time you'll do it using the<a class=\"external external-icon\" href=\"http://phaser.io/\" rel=\" noopener\">Phaser</a> HTML5 game framework. This idea here is to teach some of the fundamentals (and advantages) of working with frameworks, along with fundamental game mechanics.</dd>\n <dt id=\"2d_maze_game_with_device_orientation\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Workflows/HTML5_Gamedev_Phaser_Device_Orientation\">2D maze game with device orientation</a></dt>\n <dd>This tutorial shows how to create a 2D maze game using HTML5, incorporating fundamentals such as collision detection and sprite placement on a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. This is a mobile game that uses the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Apps/Build/gather_and_modify_data/responding_to_device_orientation_changes\">Device Orientation</a> and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Vibration_API\">Vibration</a><strong> APIs</strong> to enhance the gameplay and is built using the <a href=\"http://phaser.io/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Phaser</a> framework.</dd>\n <dt id=\"2d_platform_game_with_phaser\"><a href=\"https://mozdevs.github.io/html5-games-workshop/en/guides/platformer/start-here/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">2D platform game with Phaser</a></dt>\n <dd>This tutorial series shows how to create a simple platform game using <a href=\"http://phaser.io/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Phaser</a>, covering fundamentals such as sprites, collisions, physics, collectables, and more.</dd>\n</dl>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Ta strona zawiera poradniki, które wyróżniają wiele sposobów pracy w celu skutecznego wszelkiego rodzaju gier internetowych.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Tutorials","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Workflows for different game types","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Workflows for different game types","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Workflows for different game types","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Tutorials","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Tutorials","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Уроки","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Tutorials","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Workflows for different game types","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/games/tutorials","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/games/tutorials/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Games","title":"Tworzenie gier"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Games/Tutorials","title":"Tutorials"}],"pageTitle":"Tutorials - Tworzenie gier | MDN","noIndexing":false}}